2: Grade 2 [Moderate; OR minimal, local or non-invasive intervention indicated; OR limiting age-appropriate instrumental ADL.]
3: Grade 3 [Severe or medically significant but not immediately life-threatening; OR hospitalization or prolongation of hospitalization indicated OR disabling; limiting self-care ADL.]
4: Grade 4 [Life-threatening consequences OR urgent intervention indicated.]
